  "body": "### Description\nOnce we have Javalin updated to a version that can send event source comments, periodically send an empty comment to all event source connections so they don't time out.\n\nIt's likely sufficient to just send the blank comment every 15 seconds regardless of whether other messages are sent as the bandwidth overhead is very low.",
